{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLFormElement.reset","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/reset","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"概要","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>reset</code> はフォームを初期状態にリセットします。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>HTMLFormElement</var>.reset()\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>forms<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"myform\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">reset</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"注記","isH3":false,"content":"<p>このメソッドは、フォームのリセットボタン押下と同様の効果となります。</p>\n<p>もしフォームコントロール（※リセットボタンなど）の id 属性か name 属性の値に \"<code>reset</code>\" が指定されている場合、フォームの <code>reset</code> メソッドをマスキングしてしまうという点に注意して下さい。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-HTML/html.html#ID-76767677\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 HTML: reset</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概要","id":"summary"},{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"注記","id":"notes"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specification"}],"summary":"reset はフォームを初期状態にリセットします。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLFormElement.reset()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLFormElement.reset()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"HT